fn try_from(ty: wasmparser::FuncType) -> Result<Self, Self::Error> {

            params: ty
                .params
                .into_vec()
                .into_iter()
                .map(WasmType::try_from)
                .collect::<Result<_, Self::Error>>()?,
            returns: ty
